verbose_text: Further in vivo microdialysis analyses confirmed that deleting astroglial VMAT2 led to a ~ 23 and ~ 33% reduction in extracellular DA levels in the PFC of P25 and P40 mice, respectively (n = 6 mice, Student 's t- test, * p < 0.05; Fig. XREF_FIG; n = 3 mice each group, per day, Student 's t- test, * * * p < 0.001; * p < 0.05; Fig. XREF_FIG).
